===Noun===
'''chav''' (''plural'' '''chavs''')

#(''British, derogatory, informal'') A member of the [[underclass]] in the [[United Kingdom]], seen as [[under-educated]]; having poor taste, especially in their choice of clothes (such as fake or counterfeit [[Burberry]] check clothing), music and modified road vehicles; having interest in [[celebrity]] culture and brand presence; and having poor social skills. 

